CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 1, 1956, pg. A11 reads: "Mink, Too! - Pretty Mildred Ann Briscoe, winner in "Miss WILY" contest, is presented a natural ranch mink stole by Seymour Farber, representative for Briskm-Berk Furs, 130 S. Highland Ave. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Seymour Farber, presenting mink stole to "Miss WILY" Mildred Ann Briscoe, posed in Warner's Cinerama Theatre
